The MIT license above covers the original code written for this PicoCalc port:

  - src/main.cpp
  - src/version.h
  - src/config/board_config.h
  - src/platform/*            (LCD / keyboard / audio / UART, adapted from the
                               author's own MIT-licensed "life" project)
  - src/compat/ArduboyTones.* (original implementation of the ArduboyTones API)
  - src/compat/EEPROM.h
  - src/compat/arduino_compat.h
  - CMakeLists.txt and documentation

Some files in src/compat/ are derived from the BSD-licensed Arduboy2 and
Adafruit-GFX libraries and remain under their original licenses.  See
THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md.

The game sketch itself (e.g. BVWCVolleyball_1.01.ino by melanjet) is NOT part
of this repository.  It is downloaded from its upstream source at build time;
its copyright belongs to its respective author and is not covered here.
